  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc5\u0d9f\u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A new political party will be formed soon",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sources say that a new political alliance to be formed by several political parties will be launched around next month",
        "A special spokesman said that the alliance is being launched under the leadership of the nine coalition parties including the Jathika Nidahas Peramuna, Lanka Lanka Sama Party, Lanka Sama Samaja Party, Pivithuru Hela Urumaya, Extremist Left Front and the draft constitution of the new alliance has been finalized.",
        "He added that several flexible names have been proposed for the new alliance and no final decision has been taken yet.",
        "He said that although no final decision has been taken regarding the leadership of the UPFA, the necessary arrangements have been made for the appointment of the office bearers."
      ],
